OPTIONAL

Dr./Dra. {especialista.nombre} {especialista.apellido} Col. No. {especialista.colegiatura} I have informed this patient and / or his legal representative of the purpose and nature of the procedure described, its risks and alternatives, and the foreseeable consequences of his no performance, leaving a record in the clinical history. Likewise, they were asked about their possible allergies, the existence of other diseases or any personal pathological circumstance that could condition the performance of the treatment. This document is incorporated into the patient's medical record.
What in proof of the above I sign in  to {consentimiento.fecha_creacion}
